okup"><span data-stu-id="cda22-214">Since this will not usually be the case, the method will nearly always return `false` even if there is an object in the collection with exactly the same values in all its properties as the object passed to the **Contains** method of <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cda22-215">내용을 확인 하는 <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>를 원하는 값과 비교 하는 멤버를 각각 열거 해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cda22-215">To determine the contents of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>, you must enumerate through each of its members, comparing them with the desired value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cda22-216">예제를 참조 하십시오.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cda22-216">See the example.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="cda22-217"><xref:System.Printing.PageResolution> 클래스에는 점 인치당 X 및 Y 차원에 대 한를 지정할 수 있는 속성 및 속성 해상도로 질적 식을 제공할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cda22-217">The <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution> class has properties in which you can specify the dots-per-inch for the X and Y dimensions and a property where you can give a qualitative expression to the resolution.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="cda22-218">프린터 페이지 확인 옵션을 지원 하지 않으면 컬렉션은 비어 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cda22-218">If the printer does not support page resolution choices, the collection is empty.</span></span>  

